{"title":"西藏萨迦格言","authors":["王尧"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":10,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏萨迦格言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海不会嫌水多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金库不会嫌宝物多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们不会嫌幸福多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学者不会嫌知识多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要对自己有益，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩子的话也应该听；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要为了取得香料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野兽的肚脐〔注〕也应该要。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕这里指从獐子脐下取麝香而言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王尧选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}